said, adding, "as a mother, I feel we should do something for
children because men, during most of their meetings, hardly
discuss such issues."
</P>
<P>
The first ladies were for the first time given the platform to
articulate to the OAU summit their intentions on their
declaration on peace and humanitarian aid.
</P>
<P>
They noted that there was urgent need for Africa to
mobilize its resources for peace and humanitarian activities
rather than wait for help from international organizations.
