<HEADLINE> Nepali Crown Prince to Visit Britain Next Week </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, June 4 (Xinhua) -- Nepali Crown Prince Dipendra will
pay a week-long official visit to the United Kingdom from Sunday
at the invitation of the British government, the Foreign Ministry
said here today.
</P>
