office in London and a hydropower station in Scotland, the
ministry said.
</P>
<P>
Prince Dipendra is also expected to visit Belgium and Kuwait
before returning home on June 21, it added.
</P>
<P>
Minister Without Portfolio Sarvendra Shukla will accompany the
prince during his trip, according to the ministry.  
</P>
