<HEADLINE> German Industry Urged to Back China, Russia Into WTO </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOGNE, Germany, June 4 (Xinhua) -- World Trade Organization
(WTO) general secretary Renato Ruggiero today said he expected
German industry to support the admission of China and Russia into
the global trade body.
</P>
<P>
