cooperate on rules and standards in the communications field.
</P>
<P>
A framework is to be established for exhibiting the
achievements made by China and the EU in their application of
communications and information technology, and
technology-transfer, to promote further cooperation.
</P>
<P>
The two sides praised in their joint declaration the
successfully implemented China-EU technology cooperation projects
and demonstration projects.
</P>
<P>
Song Jian, and SSTC Vice-Minister Xu Guanhua have held formal
talks separately with Commissioner Dr. Martin Bangemann.
</P>
<P>
Dr. Martin Bangemann visiting China from June 3 to 6 at the
invitation of Song Jian.  
