Central Asian countries, the bank said here today in a news
release.
</P>
<P>
The bank recently held a meeting in Almaty, capital of
Kazakhstan, bringing together government officials from
Kazakhstan, Kirgizstan, Uzbekistan and the Xinjiang Uygur
Autonomous Region of China to establish a consensus on goals and
implementation of the regional cooperation, the news release said.
