<HEADLINE> Container Train Links Shanghai with Southwest Chinese Port </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 4 (Xinhua) -- An international container train
has pulled out of Shanghai, China's largest economic center, for
Chengdu, capital of southeast China's Sichuan Province.
</P>
