Congress (ANC) to write its own version of history about the
"tumultuous times from which we have emerged".
</P>
<P>
The IFP,representing the country's eight million Zulu tribe
population, is the biggest black opposition.
</P>
<P>
The DP is the white political party in South Africa.
</P>
