<HEADLINE> Thailand Lifts Ban on Gypsum Mining </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, June 4 (Xinhua) -- The Thai Industry Ministry has
announced its decision to revoke the ban on gypsum mining in
Thailand as the demand rises on the world market.
</P>
<P>
