<HEADLINE> Ajax to Pay Millions for Costa Rican Player </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, June 3 (Xinhua) -- 1995 European Cup champions Ajax
Amsterdam paid five million U.S. dollars for 19-year-old Costa
Rican striker Froylan Ledezma on a five-year contract on Tuesday.
</P>
